We have high-quality 738 LEDs in each strip so it no strobe and dark spot, it's brighter and smoother. Plus, the 52FT neon rope lights are long enough to be used in more places.
  • IP67 Waterproof & Wide applicationThe neon rope lights use IP67 waterproof material, they have excellent weather resistance, no matter it is windy and rainy weather or snowy days can work normally. The light tape can be used both indoor & outdoors. Decorating the living room with neon rope lights to add atmosphere while watching TV.   • 3 Ways Control & Multi modesWe offer 3 ways to you to control neon rope lights. Firstly, using the IR 44keys remote. Sencondly, the RGB+IC LED strip lights can be controlled with APP, using the APP can get the palette which offers 16million colors. Various static colors and dynamic jumping/flashing/fading modes for you to choose. It also provide 213 dynamic modes and different functions. Thirdly, can also use the 3 buttons bluetooth controller to make some simple directives to the neon lights.
  • Outstanding Safety & FlexibilityThe plug neon LED lights is ET certified, safety is guaranteed. The neon strips are touchable and won't cause any harm. We use a low-voltage 24V controller, which consumes less energy. The light strip is flodable and cuttable, it can be easily bent or shaped and cut to length to fit any space. The flexible LED light can well meet the needs of DIY. You can design your own unique patterns. Rope lights can be installed with adhesive or clips and screws.
  • Music sync & Timer & Memory functionMagic colors LED strip lights use the built-in microphone to detect audio and display the rhythm effect in real time according to the sound, this function is perfect for gamers. Would be wonderful for a friend's party. Using timer you can set what time to turn it on and off. It's nice to set it as your wake-up alarm. The memory function can store the color and mode before you turn it off, and the next time you turn it on, it will show the previous look.

En 20 metros (divididos en dos tiras de 12 metros cada una) hay una cantidad desproporcionada de LED COB que, debo admitir, encuentro mucho ms brillantes que otros LED similares que ya tengo en mi poder.       Me encanta todo lo que es luz e iluminacin, me gusta variar para darle un toque siempre diferente a mi hogar. Esta es tambin la razn por la que hoy estoy aqu para probar estas tiras LED BUNACET COB.

      El funcionamiento es muy sencillo, basta con conectar la tira a la caja de control y luego a la toma de corriente. Es posible aplicar los LED a travs del prctico adhesivo que se encuentra en la parte posterior a lo largo de toda la tira.
